OL,5, Fashion firm Boohoo has become the     
OL,6, latest retailer to charge shoppers who 
OL,7, return items.                          
OL,9,FCustomers must now pay #1.99 to return 
OL,10,Fproducts, with the cost deducted from  
OL,11,Ftheir refund. The move, first reported 
OL,12,Fby Retail Week, came into effect on 4  
OL,13,FJuly.                                  
OL,15,FBoohoo blamed the move on the rising   
OL,16,Fcost of shipping.                      
OL,18,FHigh Street firms such as Uniqlo, Next 
OL,19,Fand Zara already charge for online     
OL,20,Freturns.                               
